391
00:38:02,324 --> 00:38:05,487
Octavio, the lady is right,
this is not the right place.

392
00:38:06,395 --> 00:38:08,295
Why don't you go back to work?

393
00:38:17,673 --> 00:38:20,005
Is that thing
