394
00:38:21,744 --> 00:38:24,406
He told me he found it in the street,
but I didn't believe him.

395
00:38:25,581 --> 00:38:27,208
Superintendent,
if you let me speak to him,

396
00:38:27,282 --> 00:38:31,048
I promise to tell you
everything he tells me. Please.

397
00:38:32,721 --> 00:38:34,086
All right.

398
00:38:34,490 --> 00:38:36,151
I have to go out for a moment.

399
00:38:36,692 --> 00:38:38,626
I'll get someone
to take you to the cells,

400
00:38:39,161 --> 00:38:41,652
but then you have to tell me
everything he says.

401
00:38:41,764 --> 00:38:43,322
Yes, of course.

402
00:39:00,182 --> 00:39:02,912
It seems that the photographer
gave a false address.

403
00:39:04,486 --> 00:39:08,388
He knows I can see him, mum,
that's why he wants them to catch me.

404
00:39:10,459 --> 00:39:11,824
If I make friends with the murderer...

405
00:39:11,927 --> 00:39:15,192
